Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:02.91,mianze,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯:小囈&翠耀星  校對:小呆  時間:呆唯  後期:火貓少女  繁化:龍之戒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,地精一直不出現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是不會攻來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,千萬不能放鬆警惕哦 瑪莉艾大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,克萊斯汀帶領的先遣隊已經到習志野了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他們似乎正在向地精軍的核心部隊進發喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的戰鬥很可能會決定我們的命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟拉拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,請睜開眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,攻擊敵先鋒部隊的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大人 請帶領主力攻擊隊出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,敵方增援 丘陵巨人兩隻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,治療組前往兩側列陣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,先消滅周邊小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,主隊繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在享受…戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但為何看上去卻是如此悲傷 如此孤寂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,追逐他的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,請講
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,第5補給小隊請出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解 立即出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,請講
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是習志野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,已按計劃成功會合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:37.40,Comment,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,疾飛號已與秋葉原來的後續部隊會合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,請講
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,部隊登船後就將出發前往銚子鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,密語通信網
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去運行得很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在各小隊中設立隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,讓小隊間形成橫向聯絡網
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再設置密語通訊員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,讓小隊與總部間形成縱向聯絡網
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,通過這個方法 能讓部隊間的情報共用變得輕鬆快捷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,克萊斯汀先生他們也處於上風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼下去應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,問題是銚子鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,打贏並不難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但在戰鬥結束後 地精們肯定會四散逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,它們可能會去各處襲擊大地人的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為了防止這種情況出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要把地精大軍引至一處進行圍殲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果銚子鎮失守的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,包圍網就會被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,銚子鎮是這次作戰的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,主公你…主公你不上戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想去 但在小隊配置沒完成前我沒法離開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,明知故問…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我倫迪浩斯•寇德是萬事如意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在覺得自己簡直所向披靡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望能一直平安無事到戰鬥結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 地精什麼的只要我們齊心協力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看來這可不只一兩百啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,估計上千了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這麼多敵人同時攻入鎮上的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再讓那些孩子們冒險了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莉艾爾姐 讓我們主動出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 在它們接近小鎮前消滅它們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喵太先生 讓我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莉艾大姐 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩講幾句 振奮一下士氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝大家努力到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大家再努把力 再協助我打一戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信大家齊心協力就一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 出征！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 為了抵禦第二波進攻 我們來編班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,冬彌 我們小隊先負責後援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,城惠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就在剛才 夏季集訓班與鯊化魚人在銚子鎮發生接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人數量遠超冒險者方的60人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,至少也有上千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,局面對我們壓倒性不利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,讓疾飛號加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,等等喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在的工作是回復MP喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,直繼先生 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,旋風斬!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,冬彌變強了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 雖然他手法粗糙 稱不上技巧高明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但他還有很大的成長空間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟拉拉也是喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她以前滿腦子只想著治療
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 狼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但她現在不僅會使用攻擊技能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,還不忘召喚出僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,還有那個吟游詩人少女和那個妖術士少年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(333,437)\fs21}Bard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(587,437)\fs21}Sorcerer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,舞動之孔雀舞曲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,少女的支援就好像是看穿了少年的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,火刑柱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Burned Stake
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪浩斯則是充滿氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他將想法和感情都融進了魔法之中 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪先生 請抑制攻勢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟拉拉小姐 不用治療了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,請繼續攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,護法屏障還有8秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,實莉正努力在縱觀全域的情況下戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴之間的協作 與敵人的相對位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,交戰順序 消滅順序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這簡直就是將名為殲敵的「字句」整理成名為戰鬥的「文章」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再把它編成名為戰術的「故事」進行閱讀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這個戰鬥方式 簡直就和阿城一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,以1%為刻度 提前30秒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就是在戰鬥時預想30秒後的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,1%指的是掌握隊友的MP的量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想不看狀態畫面就完全掌握與自己職業不同的隊友的MP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,以精確到1%的程度掌握MP的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至完全掌握敵人的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,然後預測30秒後的戰況和狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,讓一切都能按自己所想的進行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是阿城的 全力管制戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Full Control Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,冬彌 後撤一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟拉拉小姐 拜託使用全體治療
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 現在遊戲變成了異世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得他應該沒法像以前那樣預測30秒後的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不過實莉的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,毫無疑問就是在模仿阿城的全力管制戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,437)\fs21}Full Control Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,實莉在追逐著城惠的背影喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道她能預測到幾秒後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這聲音 我記得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:12:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是德魯伊的特殊攻擊魔法 菇精之哭喊的聲音喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:12:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(198,437)\fs21}Druid
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:12:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(531,437)\fs21}Shrieker Echo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是我拜託瑟拉拉小姐設置來當警報用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是地精又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我們吧 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,上場咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 倫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喵太先生也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,直繼先生 地精就讓我們來解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有吟游詩人五十鈴小姐在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,437)\fs21}Bard
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,擁有持續作戰能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…喂！實莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我來負責情報監控
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(483,437)\fs21}Operator
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟拉拉小姐請集中精神治療
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但實莉你不是負責戰區偵防的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(513,437)\fs21}Filed Monitor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我來負責監管大家的MP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是地精
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,數量不少 得把它們引到一起才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但靠武士的特技效率太低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們見識見識我美妙的魔法旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,靈蛇雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Serpent Volt
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,來了來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,五十鈴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,遲鈍蝸牛之歌謠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,裂盔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,寒冰槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Frost Spear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,解…解放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Dismissal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,五十鈴小姐 有沒有看到我華麗的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是是 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼感覺像是在耍我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,騙你的啦 沒耍你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.69,Comment,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我能以5%為刻度 預測5秒後的未來 最多到10秒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒法做到城惠先生那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,居然到離鎮子那麼近的地方了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小城城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再有一小時左右疾飛號就能到你們那了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,請再堅持一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 再過一小時援兵就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大家加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪的MP…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這場戰鬥要到什麼時候結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 瑪莉艾爾小姐來聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她說載著援軍的船就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,到時就會派人來幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,還差一點 我們再努把力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 我還在想接下來要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子都餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,惡狼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看來還不止啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,助力之柳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Willow Spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,緊急魔法 四方拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟拉拉小姐 你專心對付那隻惡狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但這樣就沒人治療了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我來代替你治療
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,兩隻惡狼 加上大地精
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它們要是一齊攻過來的話冬彌就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,冬彌 你去牽制住大地精和另一隻惡狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪先生 五十鈴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,四方拜的效果還剩32秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,趁這段時間我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,遭遇數個強敵時 可用的戰略有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,先消滅較弱的個體 削減敵方數量也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因為減少對方的有生力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就能有效控制我方受到的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冰風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Frigid Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,共鳴打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Resonance Beat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,五十鈴小姐 我們快去解決另一隻惡狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,治療跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,兩隻惡狼加上大地精
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,冬彌的剩餘HP要是一直這樣減下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,9秒後冬彌就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,祓濯障壁的再使用時限還剩8秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(444,437)\fs21}Recast time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 這種程度的傷害阻絕對那種敵人沒作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果冬彌戰死的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,戰死的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,冬彌先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這隻狗崽子就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,太亂來了 倫迪你可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 五十鈴小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼會輸給這隻狗崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我倫迪浩斯•寇德可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,冒險者！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去有危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,自然重生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Nature Revive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,復活魔法不管用？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,實莉 你再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,召魂之祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪 倫迪他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,大地人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然他曾與我們一起組隊 一起冒險 一起吃飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但倫迪他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,添加好友 添加好友 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…你是大地人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,能替我保密嗎 五十鈴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要成為冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他才那麼努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼拼命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,「你不可能成為冒險者」我說不出這種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 倫迪哥是大地人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那他沒法復活了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟拉拉姐 再用一次復活魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,再使用時限還沒過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(363,437)\fs21}Recast time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我試試治療魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎在使用治療魔法後就會有些細微的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,復活魔法沒用的話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,先別放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,請救救他 拜託了 城惠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要城惠先生的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,倫迪浩斯戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他是大地人 而大地人無法復活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.83,0:24:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是這個世界的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但城惠卻向其發起挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為了實現實莉的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,為了能一同環遊世界 找尋不曾有人見過的朝霞的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.73,0:24:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.51,0:24:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 契約
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將改變世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
